data.description: Two-Story brick home in the established neighborhood of Forest Hills. Convenient playground across the street for walks or play for family members. The 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths are upstairs with a half bath downstairs off the kitchen and back door. Two bedrooms have access to a covered balcony overlooking the front of the house. Kitchen has a breakfast bar for a couple of stools PLUS a breakfast area for a small table/chairs. In addition, a formal dining room is available off the kitchen for another eating area. Nice covered porch overlooking the large, fenced backyard for your pets or private outdoor activities. Come take a look at making this your next home. Contact listing agent for more information.
